sentences: The Revd Thomas Caryl Micklem (1 August 1925 – 2 June 2003) was an English minister in the Congregational and United Reformed churches, hymn writer and religious broadcaster.
He was accredited a minister of the Congregational Church in 1949 and ordained in 1952.
